{"tid":1263042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林忌：香港很多抗爭者的態度很脫離現實","createTime":"2019-06-28T03:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T04:27:24.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04b0aa4cec381664fcc66e870b88fd6547997059","tid":1263042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156042345346121&amp;id=700986120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156042345346121%26id%3D700986120&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5cd970b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156042345346121&amp;id=700986120</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n6月24日 16:00<br />\n<br />\n其實從香港人簽聯署的態度，就知道點解香港會搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong>要求美國「解放香港」這種完全不可能實現的聯署，就簽名滿十萬個；要求制裁香港官員，拒絕其入境簽證的聯署，這種美國政府完全可以做得到的聯署，就簽得果四萬幾個</strong>；有些人成日屈別人「消散民氣」，最叻「消散民氣」的，咪就係搞個冇意義的聯署囉<br />\n<br />\n如果你相信白宮聯署有用，咁你覺得取消港官的簽證機會高D，定係美軍出兵解放香港的機會高D呢？不如咁啦，搞個「香港發大財」的聯署，要求美國總統對每個香港人派一百萬美金啦，簽啦簽啦"},{"pid":"f5bd0766e4428deffa19e7e37106eab4bf7ebe88","tid":1263042,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"佢講得無錯<br />\n<br />\n香港人要求外國幫助， 態度唔該現實d<br />\n<br />\n(黃台仰係德國都要暫不提倡港獨)"},{"pid":"3a869e1ade1489c60dcf3b88551f385f557c6569","tid":1263042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26889a9d2d3572a4636c3686c702bf784002255","tid":1263042,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"香港發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7c9e3742a823202ac9a234ec362203726a4002","tid":1263042,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"聯署link<br />\